uity loan terms after origination? Refinancing home equity loans works similarly to refinancing first mortgages:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How do home equity loans work for recently purchased properties?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Can you access equity shortly after buying a home? Yes, though limitations often apply:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What recourse do lenders have if you default on home equity loans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What happens if you stop making home equity loan payments? Secured debt means lenders have specific remedies:"}}]};
